{
  "stem": "22944.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my father came one day at home, and I suppose he knew from the Synagogue or from the Jewish center that he used to go to, and his finances has been confiscated.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we had to move, fairly quickly, to another place, what presumably, my mother arranged with her sisters.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to Nitra, what was about 50 kilometers from Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do remember that journey, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, we had to sort of huddle up very quickly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think there was some kind of lorry who took our stuff, our belongings-- our household goods.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we moved to a place-- what I presume my mother must have arranged it with her sister, to a place-- a street called [INAUDIBLE] 28.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was a small town, Nitra.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't-- I presume-- I don't think so, because the cottage-- the bungalow we moved to was quite small.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was only a two-room one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they put as much as they could in a table and beds and a few furniture-- as much as they could to squeeze into that little place.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the rest, I suppose, my mother sold or left behind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do you know, it's a strange thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it wasn't the Victorian period, but the times are so bad that children were seen but not heard.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So as a child, I don't think that I had very much opinion to express what I want.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used to cry quite a bit and, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] possibly wanted love and attention like any other child.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think our parents were very kind, very good people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, they gave us as much as they could, but I wasn't the only one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I about was six or seven, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
